  "about": {
    "details": "<p>Incorporated in 2021, Shoora Designs Limited is engaged in the business of manufacturing and trading diamonds and jewelry.</p>\n<p>The company manufactures natural diamonds and jewelry mainly focusing on Natural Lab Grown Diamond and Jewelry.</p>\n<p>Shoora procures natural diamonds through suppliers and outsources cleaving, laser cutting, and polishing services from local job-workers in the domestic market of Surat while planning and mapping rough diamonds remain in-house. Its major clients come from wholesalers and retailers with business concentration predominantly in Surat, Gujarat, and Mumbai, Maharashtra.</p>\n<p>Shoora Designs' jewelry is available on both offline market and online platforms.</p>\n<p>The company recorded Rs. 105.58 lacks revenue from operations for the nine-month period ended March 31, 2023, and Rs. 162.58 lacks for the Financial Year ended March 31, 2022.</p>"
  },
