  "faqs": [
    {
      "question": "What is the Shoora Designs IPO?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>Shoora Designs IPO<!-- --> is a <b>SME<!-- --> <!-- -->IPO<!-- --> of <!-- -->424000<!-- --> equity shares</b> of the face value of ₹<!-- -->10<!-- --> aggregating up to ₹<!-- -->2.03<!-- --> Crores. The issue is priced at <span>₹48 per share</span>. The minimum order quantity is <!-- -->3000<!-- -->.</p><p>The <!-- -->IPO<!-- --> <b>opens on <!-- -->August 17, 2023</b>, and <b>closes on <!-- -->August 21, 2023</b>.</p><p>Kfin Technologies Limited<!-- --> is the registrar for the <!-- -->IPO<!-- -->. The shares are proposed to be listed on <!-- -->BSE SME<!-- -->.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "How to apply in Shoora Designs IPO through Zerodha?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>Zerodha customers can apply online in <!-- -->Shoora Designs IPO<!-- --> using UPI as a payment gateway. Zerodha customers can apply in <!-- -->Shoora Designs IPO<!-- --> by login into Zerodha Console (back office) and submitting an IPO application form.</p><p><strong>Steps to apply in <!-- -->Shoora Designs IPO<!-- --> through Zerodha</strong></p><ol><li>Visit the Zerodha website and login to Console.</li><li>Go to Portfolio and click the IPOs link.</li><li>Go to the '<!-- -->Shoora Designs IPO<!-- -->' row and click the 'Bid' button.</li><li>Enter your UPI ID, Quantity, and Price.</li><li>Submit IPO application form.</li><li>Visit the UPI App (net banking or BHIM) to approve the mandate.</li></ol><p>Visit <a href=\"/broker/zerodha/ipo/18/\" title=\"Zerodha IPO Application Process Review\">Zerodha IPO Application Process Review</a> for more detail.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "When Shoora Designs IPO will open?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>The Shoora Designs IPO opens on August 17, 2023 and closes on August 21, 2023.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "What is the lot size of Shoora Designs IPO?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>Shoora Designs IPO<!-- --> <b>lot size is <!-- -->3000</b>, and the <b>minimum amount required is <span>₹1,44,000</span></b>.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "How to apply for Shoora Designs IPO?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>You can apply in <!-- -->Shoora Designs IPO<!-- --> online using either <a href=\"/article/upi-payment-option-ipo-application-explained/382/\">UPI</a> or ASBA as a payment method. ASBA IPO application is available in the net banking of your bank account. UPI IPO application is offered by brokers who don't offer banking services. Read more detail about applying IPO online through <a href=\"/broker/zerodha/ipo/18/\" title=\"Zerodha IPO Review\"><b>Zerodha</b></a>, <a href=\"/broker/upstox/ipo/33/\" title=\"Upstox IPO Review\">Upstox</a>, <a href=\"/broker/5paisa/ipo/4/\" title=\"5Paisa IPO Review\">5Paisa</a>, <a href=\"/broker/edelweiss_broking/ipo/34/\" title=\"Nuvama IPO Review\">Nuvama</a>, <a href=\"/broker/hdfc-securities/ipo/6/\" title=\"HDFC Bank IPO Review\">HDFC Bank</a>, and <a href=\"/broker/sbi-capital/ipo/19/\" title=\"SBI Capital IPO Review\">SBI Bank</a>.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "When is Shoora Designs IPO allotment?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>The finalization of Basis of Allotment for <!-- -->Shoora Designs IPO<!-- --> will be done on <!-- -->Thursday, August 24, 2023<!-- -->, and the allotted shares will be credited to your demat account by <!-- -->Monday, August 28, 2023<!-- -->. Check the <a href=\"/ipo_allotment_status/shoora-designs-ipo/1483/\" title=\"Shoora Designs IPO Allotment Status\">Shoora Designs IPO<!-- --> allotment status</a>.</p></div>"
    },
